comment:
* Information you can retrieve about a particular system
 * module.

variables.name: mPackageName
variables.comment: The package name of this module.

variables.name: mApexModuleName
variables.comment:
* The name of the APEX this module is distributed as, or null if it is not distributed via
     * APEX.

variables.name: mHidden
variables.comment: Whether or not this module is hidden from the user.

variables.name: mApkInApexPackageNames
variables.comment:
* The list of the package names of all APK-in-APEX apps in the module, or
     * null if there are none.

methods.name: public ModuleInfo setName(CharSequence name)
methods.comment: @hide Sets the public name of this module.

methods.name: public CharSequence getName()
methods.comment: Gets the public name of this module.

methods.name: public ModuleInfo setPackageName(String packageName)
methods.comment: @hide Sets the package name of this module.

methods.name: public String getPackageName()
methods.comment: Gets the package name of this module.

methods.name: public ModuleInfo setHidden(boolean hidden)
methods.comment: @hide Sets whether or not this package is hidden.

methods.name: public boolean isHidden()
methods.comment: Gets whether or not this package is hidden.

methods.name: public ModuleInfo setApkInApexPackageNames(@NonNull Collection<String> apkInApexPackageNames)
methods.comment: @hide Set the list of the package names of all APK-in-APEX apps in this module.

methods.name: public Collection<String> getApkInApexPackageNames()
methods.comment: @hide Get the list of the package names of all APK-in-APEX apps in the module.

methods.name: public String toString()
methods.comment: Returns a string representation of this object.

methods.name: public int describeContents()
methods.comment: Describes the kinds of special objects contained in this object.

methods.name: public void writeToParcel(Parcel dest, int parcelableFlags)
methods.comment: Flattens this object into the given {@link Parcel}.
